# EduVision AI — Implementation Plan

## Overview

EduVision AI is a **multi-role intelligent academic platform** designed for universities. It serves three distinct user types — **Students**, **Teachers**, and **Authorities** (VC/Dean/Department Head) — each with their own entry flow, dashboard, and AI-driven analytics. This plan covers the full implementation from project setup to all four modules.

The stack is **Next.js 14 (App Router) + Tailwind CSS + Recharts** per the spec requirements. All data is static/dummy JSON at this stage, structured for easy API replacement later.

