## Proposed Changes

### Phase 0 — Project Bootstrap

#### [NEW] Next.js 14 Project Scaffold
- Run `npx create-next-app@latest ./` with TypeScript, Tailwind, App Router
- Install: `recharts`, `lucide-react`, `framer-motion`, `clsx`

---

### Phase 1 — Entry Flow

#### [NEW] Splash Screen (`app/page.tsx`)
- Animated EduVision AI logo with pulse/glow
- 3-second auto-redirect to `/role-selection`
- Dark background with particle/gradient animation

#### [NEW] Role Selection (`app/role-selection/page.tsx`)
- 3 glassmorphism cards: Student | Teacher | Authority
- Icon + title + short description per card
- Hover animation (lift + glow)
- Click → saves role to context + localStorage → navigates to `/login/{role}`

#### [NEW] Login Pages (×3)
- Role-specific themed login form (different accent color per role)
- Email + Password fields
- Simulated auth (dummy credentials in JSON)
- On success → redirects to `/dashboard/{role}`

---

### Phase 2 — Global Context & Layout

#### [NEW] `context/AppContext.tsx`
- Stores: `role`, `user`, `isAuthenticated`
- Exposes `login()`, `logout()`, `setRole()`
- Reads from `localStorage` for session persistence

#### [NEW] Role-aware Layout Wrappers
- Each dashboard group wrapped in its own layout with sidebar + top nav
- Sidebar items differ per role
- Sidebar collapses on mobile

---

### Phase 3 — Student Module (9 pages)

#### [NEW] `data/student.json`
Fields: profile, subjects (name, marks, attendance, assignments), extracurricular (clubs, events, roles), skills (radar scores), peers (class average, percentile), alerts, mentor recommendation.

#### [NEW] AI Engine — Student (`utils/aiEngine.ts`)
Rules:
- `attendance < 75` → Low Attendance Alert
- `subjectScore < 60` → Weak Subject
- `communication < 60` → Suggest debate club
- `leadership < 60` → Suggest leadership role
- `gpa < 2.5` → Academic risk alert

#### Pages:
1. **`/dashboard/student`** — Overview cards (GPA, attendance, alerts), performance line chart, AI recommendations widget
2. **`/student/academic`** — Subject table with marks/attendance, weak subject highlight, trend chart
3. **`/student/extracurricular`** — Club cards, event participation, skill mapping
4. **`/student/skills`** — Radar chart for 5 skills, strengths vs gaps analysis
5. **`/student/ai-advisor`** — Personalized recommendation cards with priority badges
6. **`/student/alerts`** — Alert list: problem + action + priority color
7. **`/student/peer-benchmark`** — Bar chart: student vs class avg, percentile badge
8. **`/student/mentor`** — Recommended teacher card with match reason
9. **`/student/profile`** — Student info card

---

### Phase 4 — Teacher Module (9 pages)

#### [NEW] `data/teacher.json`
Fields: profile, courses (code, name, students, avg marks, attendance, risk), studentList (segmented by performance), alerts, AI suggestions, mentees, skill gap data.

#### AI Rules — Teacher:
- Many students score < 60 in same topic → suggest extra class
- Course attendance < 75 → attendance warning
- At-risk group > 30% → suggest mentoring session

#### Pages:
1. **`/dashboard/teacher`** — Course summary, at-risk count, class performance, alerts
2. **`/teacher/courses`** — Course cards with risk level badge
3. **`/teacher/students`** — Full student table with filter (High/Average/At-Risk)
4. **`/teacher/at-risk`** — At-risk student cards with problem + suggestion
5. **`/teacher/course-analytics`** — Per-course performance trends, topic weakness
6. **`/teacher/ai-advisor`** — Teaching suggestion cards
7. **`/teacher/mentorship`** — Assigned mentee cards with focus area
8. **`/teacher/skill-gap`** — Class radar chart + individual student skill view
9. **`/teacher/alerts`** — Priority alert list

---

### Phase 5 — Authority Module (10 pages)

#### [NEW] `data/authority.json`
Fields: profile (role: vc/dean/dept-head), university stats, departments array (name, students, GPA avg, attendance, at-risk, skills), teachers array, course health, skill overview, reports, strategic suggestions.

#### AI Rules — Authority:
- Dept avg GPA < 2.5 → department support alert
- At-risk % > 30% → mentoring program suggestion
- Communication avg < 60% → workshop suggestion
- Attendance trend dropping → policy review suggestion

#### Pages:
1. **`/dashboard/authority`** — University KPI cards, dept performance chart, institutional alerts, strategic suggestions
2. **`/authority/departments`** — Department cards with health indicators
3. **`/authority/department-comparison`** — Multi-bar chart comparing departments across all metrics
4. **`/authority/teachers`** — Teacher effectiveness table/cards
5. **`/authority/student-insights`** — Population breakdown, common weak areas
6. **`/authority/institutional-alerts`** — Institutional-level alert list
7. **`/authority/ai-strategic-advisor`** — Strategic recommendation cards with expected impact
8. **`/authority/course-health`** — Course/program health table with risk indicators
9. **`/authority/skill-overview`** — University radar + dept-wise skill comparison
10. **`/authority/reports`** — Report selector + UI-rendered summary

