## Open Questions

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Dummy Credentials** — Should each role have a single shared credential (e.g., `student@edu.ai / password123`) or multiple accounts per role? I'll default to one credential per role unless told otherwise.

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Authority Sub-roles** — The spec mentions VC/Dean/Dept Head see different views. Should the single authority login determine which sub-role they get, or should there be a sub-role selector? I'll implement a single authority user that sees the full VC-level view by default.

> [!NOTE]
> **Charts Library** — The spec suggests Recharts (via React). I'll use Recharts for all charts (Line, Bar, Radar, Pie) for consistency.

> [!NOTE]
> **Mobile Responsiveness** — All dashboards will be responsive with a collapsible sidebar for mobile. Priority is desktop-first as this is a data-heavy analytics platform.

